/*
 * adam_update.comp â€” Adam optimizer per-parameter update
 *
 * Bindings: 0=params (R+W), 1=grads (R), 2=m (R+W), 3=v (R+W)
 * Push constants: p0=count, f0=lr, f1=beta1, f2=beta2, f3=eps, f4=bc1, f5=bc2
 *
